msgstr "$second_password_1|!"

#. [option]: speaker=Arne
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/3_Guarded_Castle.cfg:438
#: data/campaigns/Two_Brothers/scenarios/3_Guarded_Castle.cfg:554
